Name: Soukaku's Namecard
Desc: Get by unlocking Soukaku's Mindscape: Attendance Meal Allowance
Desc2:
A card with a member of Section 6 printed on it.
While having a lot of commemorative value, this card has almost no practical use. Even if Soukaku could actually be contacted with it, her "guardian" in the squad would once again filter out the commissions she can take on.
